## Basic Switch Configuration
```
enable
conf t
hostname SW
no ip domain-lookup
enable secret cisco
username admin secret cisco
line console 0
logging synchronous
login local
exit
line vty 0 15
login local
transport input ssh
exit
service password-encryption
banner motd $Authorized access only$
end
```

### SSH V2
