## Trunk Configuration

### Core Switch — Root Bridge
```
spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst
spanning-tree vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100 root primary

interface range gi1/0/1 - 4
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100
switchport nonegotiate
```

### Secondary Switch
```
spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst
spanning-tree vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100 root secondary

interface range gi0/1 - 2
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100
switchport nonegotiate

interface range fa0/5 - 6
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100
switchport nonegotiate
```

### Default Switch
```
spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst

interface range gi0/1 - 2
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100
switchport nonegotiate

interface range fa0/5 - 6
switchport mode trunk
