## EtherChannel — LACP

### Configure Port-Channel first
```
interface port-channel 1
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100
switchport nonegotiate
```

### Then physical interfaces
```
interface range gi0/1 - 2
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 1,10,20,30,40,50,99,100
switchport nonegotiate
channel-group 1 mode active
```

